name: PyNano
Feature:
Create the new Pyqt5 branch and never update anymore.
 The new update will replace the PyQt5 by PySide2.
Feature:
 Support for Python 3.8.
 Please conduct the cmd .
 'pip install -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple PySide2'. 
 For new version: git pull origin master 
 For PyQt5 Version: git pull origin pyqt5
